    <item>
      <title>美国银行 Swiber 表示，国债收益率可实现 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/5-treasury-yield-achievable-bofa-s-swiber-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行美国利率策略主管梅根·斯维伯(Meghan Swiber)表示，如果美联储重新考虑加息，美国国债收益率可能会达到5%。她在彭博电视台发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/5-treasury-yield-achievable-bofa-s-swiber-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 21:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登新规意味着紧凑型荧光灯泡将被淘汰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/new-biden-rule-means-lights-out-for-compact-fluorescent-bulbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紧凑型荧光灯泡——曾经被认为是清洁能源转型的螺旋形标志​​——根据周五敲定的拜登政府规则，该规则将有效地逐步淘汰，该规则对最常用的照明类型提出了新的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/new-biden-rule-means-lights-out-for-compact-fluorescent-bulbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 21:08:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对在交易所使用俄罗斯金属实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-imposes-sanctions-on-use-of-russian-metals-on-exchanges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和英国宣布对俄罗斯铝、铜和镍的贸易实行新的限制，以遏制俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京为其战争机器提供资金的能力，此举可能会扰乱全球金属市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-imposes-sanctions-on-use-of-russian-metals-on-exchanges</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 20:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币的暴跌引发了看涨押注的“一连串清算”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bitcoin-declines-as-the-liquidation-of-bullish-bets-accelerate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币一度出现一个多月来的最大跌幅，引发了一系列投机性加密货币头寸的清算，导致 Solana、Cardano 和 Polkadot 等规模较小的数字资产暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bitcoin-declines-as-the-liquidation-of-bullish-bets-accelerate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 19:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战争不安情绪加剧，股市受到打击，市场纷纷涌向债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[地缘政治风险的爆发扰乱了金融世界，导致股市下跌——同时刺激资金流向债券和美元等市场最安全的角落。石油上涨。]]></description>
